Building_5_Level_4_ROOM__STUDENT_ACTIVIT.Description: Student Activity Centre is located in Building 5 Level 4, and is a common space in SUTD for students to use for their activities, be it club or academic. The room mainly serves as storage for SUTD clubs and interest groups, in the form of lockers and rooms. Apply with Office of Student Life (OSL) for club storage space. Air conditioned, and can be accessed by student red card, closing time approximately 2300.
